\newlabel{fig:trends}{{2}{10}{ORC advantage trends. (a)~NK landscapes: min-ORC vs.\ random direction success rate as a function of epistasis $K$, for both $N\!=\!16$ (solid) and $N\!=\!20$ (dotted). (b)~W-model: same comparison as a function of epistasis $\nu $. The ORC advantage is consistent across problem sizes}{figure.1.2}{}}
