\newlabel{tab:correlation}{{2}{10}{Spearman rank correlations ($\rho $) between landscape metrics and algorithm performance across all 420 $N\!=\!16$ instances with $>1$ local optimum. $^{***}$: $p < 0.001$. The best value in each column is \textbf {bolded}}{table.1.2}{}}
